<HL>
   Software Glitches Cripple
   Parts of 2 Phone Systems
   ----
   By Mary Lu Carnevale
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/27/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A10
</SO>
